data.description: Spotless Antigua floor plan is large, bright and open. The beautiful manicured trees and lawn welcome you into this well maintained home featuring Two bedrooms, a dining room, living room and enough room for an office.  The Florida room over looks the landscaped rear yard.  Granite counters, raised toilets, neutral colors and laundry area make this ready to move in to. Recent updates include freshly painted interior and exterior, newer roof (2014), A/C (2017), Floors (2019), guest bath (2023), and water heater (2022). If you're looking for a single family home where there is no need to worry about the lawn,this is the home for you. Just relax and enjoy your time off, go play golf, tennis, take a swim. This community offers it all; Pools, baseball, exercise equipment, lapidary, sewing, arts, crafts, computers. It offers bus transportation, security patrols,emergency services and many more features that provide a health and recreational lifestyle and much more. This home is located just blocks from the banks, shopping, churches, coffee shops, restaurants, doctor offices. A move to the Sun City Center, Florida area is a central move close to the beaches, airport, Disney, Sea World, Busch Gardens, and more.
